gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 113, Heat 92
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeat the Heat, 113-92. Klay Thompson led the way with 28 points and six 3PT FG for the Warriors, while Jonathan Kuminga (18 points, seven rebounds) and Stephen Curry (17 points, six assists) added a combined 35 points in the victory. Bam Adebayo tallied 24 points, nine rebounds and five assists for the Heat in the losing effort. The Warriors improve to 37-34 on the season, while the Heat fall to 39-33.
